\v 32 If the bull gores a male servant or a female servant, thirty shekels\f + A shekel is about 10 grams or about 0.35 ounces, so 30 shekels is about 300 grams or about 10.6 ounces.\f* of silver shall be given to their master, and the ox shall be stoned.
